01:33:17.119 --> 01:33:17.660
- No problem.

01:33:17.660 --> 01:33:19.243
- Just hear their
questions and then--

01:33:19.243 --> 01:33:21.280
- Yeah, I'll take
all your questions

01:33:21.280 --> 01:33:23.430
and I'll write down
my yes/no answers.

